BUY BUY BABY Buy Buy Baby , Inc.
( stylized : buybuy BABY ) is an American chain of stores that sell clothing , strollers and other items for use with infants and young children .
It operates 135 stores across the United States and Canada .
The chain was founded in 1996 by brothers Richard and Jeffrey Feinstein .
It consisted of eight stores when it was acquired by Bed Bath & Beyond in 2007 .
Its primary competitor was Babies " R " Us .
